ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Nááts'ihch'oh National Park Reserve) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (NAATS'IHCH'OH NATIONAL PARK RESERVE) ORDER which withdraws from disposal certain tracts of territorial lands in order to facilitate the establishment of proposed Naats'ihch'oh National Park Reserve within the Sahtu Settlement Area in the Northwest Territories.
